<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM4.4">
<l>oṇpavaḷa vēlai yulavutaṇ pāṟkaṭaluḷ</l>
<l>kaṇṭuyilu māyōṉ kaḻaliṇaikaḷ kāṇpataṟku</l>
<l>paṇpakarum vaṇṭiṉaṅkaḷ paṇpāṭum vēṅkaṭattuc</l>
<l>ceṇpakamāy niṟkun tiruvuṭaiyē ṉāvēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I will possess the wealth of standing as a campaka-tree</l>
<l rend="indent">in Veṅkaṭa, where the music-uttering swarms of bees hum the paṇ melody</l>
<l>for the sake of seeing the pair of [feet with] anklets of Māyōṉ,</l>
<l>who sleeps inside the cool milk ocean which moves [and brings] radiant red corals to the shores.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
